    public abstract class BaseHttpResource
extends BaseNetworkResource
    A network resource accessible via HTTP.

    Content

    The content of an HTTP resource can be accessed using any of the methods inherited by all resources. An HTTP resource also has:

    • contentType() - A MIME content type
    • content() - The resource content as a string
    • encoding() - A content encoding
    • header(String) - An optional header
    • status() - A status code once the resource has been accessed
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
